---
import "/src/styles/style.css";
---

<div class="BackgroundFeature relative" id="feature">
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <div class="first-f-text">
        <h2>Events // Circular Lab</h2>
        <p>Følg med her i kalenderen og hold dig opdateret på, hvad der sker i Circular Lab. Vejledninger, foredrag, events og lignende vil løbende blive lagt ind i kalenderen.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="second-f-text">
        <h3>Circular Lab - Repair Café</h3>
        <p class="dato">9. April 2025 // 14:00 - 16:00</p>
        <p>
          I Circular Lab arbejder vi med cirkulære løsninger. På denne workshop har vi fokus på lapning af tekstiler – kom og lær, hvordan du kan forlænge levetiden på dit tøj med en nål, tråd og lidt
          kreativitet.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-image">
        <img src="/images/reparcafeposter.png" alt="Repair Café Poster" />
      </div>
      <a href="/events">
        <button class="cta">SE HELE KALENDEREN</button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative moss image -->
  <img src="/images/IMG_9572 1.png" alt="" class="MOSS" />
</div>

<style>
  a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .feature-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .feature-text p,
  .feature-text h2 {
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .first-f-text {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .BackgroundFeature {
    background-color: #ff671f;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative; /* ✅ Makes absolute child position correctly */
  }

  .MOSS {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -12rem;
    right: 0;
    width: 45%; /* Increase from 35% */
    max-width: 300px;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 2rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: block; /* Makes the button take full line width */
    margin: 2rem auto; /* Top/bottom = 1rem, left/right = auto (centers it) */
    border: 2px solid black;
    background: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: black;
    color: white;
    transition: ease 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-image img {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 70%; /* ✅ limits image to 70% of its container */
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }
  /* Desktop view */
  @media screen and (min-width: 800px) {
    .BackgroundFeature {
      background-color: #ff671f;
      padding: 4rem;
    }
    .MOSS {
      bottom: -10rem;
      right: 0rem;
      width: 50%;
      max-width: 270px;
    }
    .feature-grid {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-text {
      width: 60%;
      padding-right: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-image {
      width: 35%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center; /* vertically center the image */
    }

    .feature-image img {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      max-height: 70%; /* ✅ limits image to 70% of its container */
      object-fit: contain;
      border-radius: 1rem;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    h3 {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
